# GitFlow Branching Strategy for TemplateMaker (PR-Based)

## Branch Structure

- main: Production-ready code. Only merge from develop or hotfix branches via Pull Requests.
- develop: Integration branch for features. All feature branches are created from and merged back to this branch via Pull Requests.
- feature/*: Feature branches for new functionality. Created from develop and merged back to develop via Pull Requests.
- release/*: Release preparation branches. Created from develop and merged to both main and develop via Pull Requests.
- hotfix/*: Hotfix branches for urgent production fixes. Created from main and merged to both main and develop via Pull Requests.
